title: Rise of the female breadwinner stalls as men see pay packets grow
text: Women's Business Rise of the female breadwinner stalls as men see pay packets grow Setback for feminism but days of the working father and stay-at-home mother as ‘default’ family are over, says think-tank study The rise of the female breadwinner has stalled Photo: SOPHIA SPRING By John Bingham , Social Affairs Editor 7:00AM BST 20 Oct 2015
